name: THE GIFT
description: This Rare Illustration made in more that 50 hours with a thousand of brush strokes. I keep this in 10 edition to remain its rarity and for the collectors to have an opportunity to invest. this piece is 3800 x 4800 pixels to remain the good quality for printing for display. the tiny gifts of pollen to a bee is a miracle and absolutely inconceivable that wonders the humanity.
